==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Paroxysmal
<hw>Par`ox*ys"mal</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Of the nature of
a paroxysm; characterized or accompanied by paroxysms; <as>as, a
<ex>paroxysmal</ex> pain; <ex>paroxysmal</ex> temper.</as></def> --
<wordforms><wf>Par`ox*ys"mal*ly</wf>, <pos>adv.</pos></wordforms>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Paroxytone</ent>⟦br⟧
